[And you're so handsome.]

00:41:10.800 --> 00:41:10.820
This dessert is like you. It's pretty and delicious.

00:41:10.820 --> 00:41:14.350
[Forcing out a girly tone]

00:41:14.620 --> 00:41:16.260
[Yoon Namno: This is too girly.]

00:41:16.260 --> 00:41:17.780
[Yoon Namno: This is too girly.
This should be more manly.]

