Should I write, "Did you eat well?"

00:41:18.440 --> 00:41:20.680
[Did you eat well?]

00:41:20.680 --> 00:41:21.700
[Jung Hae-in, did you eat well?]
[Freely changes pretend-personality]

00:41:21.700 --> 00:41:23.850
Shooting commercials must have been hard work.

00:41:23.850 --> 00:41:25.580
Share it with the staff.

00:41:25.960 --> 00:41:27.410
From your Manito bro.

00:41:27.870 --> 00:41:30.180
