00:41:30.180 --> 00:41:32.210
[Please take good care of Hae-in] [Financier]
[I'm also done with the note for the staff’s snacks.]

00:41:32.210 --> 00:41:33.790
I’ll write one more to express my feelings.

00:41:33.790 --> 00:41:36.320
[These snacks are for the staff!] [Financier]
[I'm also done with the note for the staff’s snacks.]

00:41:37.090 --> 00:41:38.260
[Should we go now?]

00:41:38.260 --> 00:41:39.430
More or less.

00:41:40.930 --> 00:41:43.770
[Ah... I suddenly feel so stressed.]

00:41:44.310 --> 00:41:49.110
[What if I panic? Well, how should I put it?
I'm really flustered when I'm panicking.]

00:41:49.120 --> 00:41:51.630
[Naturally speaking in a flustered manner]

00:41:51.980 --> 00:41:53.630
[Ah... So nervous]

00:41:54.310 --> 00:41:55.850
[Shaking]

00:41:57.070 --> 00:42:01.090
[Puts the sticker on with shaking hands]

00:42:02.080 --> 00:42:03.130
[Tidies up appearance one last time]

00:42:03.130 --> 00:42:04.430
Why am I so nervous?

00:42:05.860 --> 00:42:08.960
[Off to the shooting site]

00:42:11.940 --> 00:42:11.950
[I think it's here?]

00:42:11.950 --> 00:42:13.550
The address seems to be here.

00:42:15.560 --> 00:42:18.000
[Swiftly]

00:42:18.640 --> 00:42:18.850
[Leaves the bag outside for now]

00:42:18.850 --> 00:42:21.980
