Just hide one behind the box.

00:42:21.980 --> 00:42:25.760
[Carefully enters the building]

00:42:26.800 --> 00:42:29.560
[Successfully sneaks into the building]

00:42:30.540 --> 00:42:31.230
[Sighs...]

00:42:33.450 --> 00:42:34.160
[Sighs...]

00:42:34.530 --> 00:42:37.270
[Conceals face]

00:42:37.840 --> 00:42:38.890
[Seriously. Why am I so nervous?]

00:42:38.890 --> 00:42:40.690
I thought this wouldn't happen.

00:42:43.760 --> 00:42:44.700
The door is open.

00:42:45.750 --> 00:42:50.630
