00:43:23.870 --> 00:43:27.900
[Hae-in, oblivious, enters the lounge]

00:43:28.870 --> 00:43:30.020
[Hides in the elevator]

00:43:30.020 --> 00:43:30.750
First floor.

00:43:33.900 --> 00:43:34.180
[Coward Namno]

00:43:34.180 --> 00:43:35.600
The door is closing.

00:43:37.540 --> 00:43:39.930
