00:43:40.710 --> 00:43:43.250
[What?] [Yoon Namno: Do you have a moment?]

00:43:43.250 --> 00:43:45.140
[What?] [De- Delivey- Delivery...]

00:43:45.150 --> 00:43:45.520
-Are you a deliveryman? -Yes.

00:43:45.520 --> 00:43:46.780
[Wait, I'll deliver it later(?)]
[The manito disguised as a deliveryman.]

00:43:46.780 --> 00:43:47.440
What is it?

00:43:47.440 --> 00:43:49.360
Wait, no, I'll deliver it later.

00:43:49.360 --> 00:43:52.060
[Rejecting delivery suddenly]

00:43:52.060 --> 00:43:53.610
[Why are the staff walking around here?]

00:43:53.610 --> 00:43:58.460
[Note: This is the commercial shooting site]

00:43:59.640 --> 00:44:02.460
[Deliveryman Catfish strikes again]

00:44:03.660 --> 00:44:08.970
[Suddenly enters calmly and puts it at the door]

00:44:09.290 --> 00:44:11.920
[Too nervous]
[Leaves without pasting on the letters to the staff]

00:44:13.210 --> 00:44:14.310
[Run]

00:44:14.310 --> 00:44:15.650
It went to the 2nd floor.

00:44:17.890 --> 00:44:21.450
[A sudden great escape]

00:44:21.880 --> 00:44:25.000
[Rushing up the stairs]

00:44:25.710 --> 00:44:29.420
[Silence]

00:44:31.780 --> 00:44:35.000
[One-way cat-and-mouse chase]

00:44:36.230 --> 00:44:39.060
[Breathing heavily with gills]

00:44:39.660 --> 00:44:42.600
[Carrying the bag and running away] [Ahh!]

00:44:42.600 --> 00:44:45.750
[Carrying the bag and running away]

00:44:47.150 --> 00:44:51.150
[Enjoying the thrill alone and returning safely]

00:44:53.190 --> 00:44:53.730
Wait.

00:44:53.730 --> 00:44:56.770
[A state of physical and mental exhaustion]

00:44:56.770 --> 00:44:57.630
Ah, just now...

00:44:59.210 --> 00:45:02.940
[I feel like I died a little...]

00:45:03.910 --> 00:45:08.060
[Really, I almost... I shouldn't say this, but...]

00:45:09.590 --> 00:45:09.630
[I almost soiled my pants]

00:45:09.630 --> 00:45:11.080
I almost soiled my pants. Seriously. I was so nervous.

00:45:11.080 --> 00:45:12.210
There's water here.

00:45:13.290 --> 00:45:17.980
[Gritted his teeth and accomplished a major task]

00:45:18.270 --> 00:45:18.730
