00:46:51.730 --> 00:46:52.390
[Appetizing sesame oil,
and a sprinkle of salt]

00:46:52.390 --> 00:46:54.020
Pour more sesame oil.

00:46:57.330 --> 00:47:00.440
[Hong Jinkyung: Make it delicious enough
to eat just the rice by itself.]

00:47:00.610 --> 00:47:01.330
Then, dice the cucumbers and put them in.

00:47:01.330 --> 00:47:05.720
[The main character of gimbap: Cucumbers.
Put the cucumbers in it]

