Season it.

00:47:07.870 --> 00:47:10.740
[Sesame salt—the more, the better]

00:47:11.520 --> 00:47:16.570
[Sesame ground by hand!]

00:47:17.000 --> 00:47:17.040
[Self-praising: This is
what handmade is all about, right?]

00:47:17.040 --> 00:47:19.370
This is what handmade is all about, right?

00:47:20.850 --> 00:47:20.910
I really sprinkled a lot of ground sesame.

00:47:20.910 --> 00:47:22.890
[Full of handmade ground sesame too]

