00:49:47.530 --> 00:49:49.330
[Vanilla bean custard]

00:49:49.330 --> 00:49:51.010
Put it into the mille-feuille.

00:49:51.010 --> 00:49:51.180
Wow, it's tiring, but it's fun.

00:49:51.180 --> 00:49:54.640
[Yoon Namno: Wow!
