00:53:07.020 --> 00:53:09.690
[Exits calmly]

00:53:09.950 --> 00:53:12.370
[Jung Hae-in]

00:53:14.030 --> 00:53:15.460
[Sprints away]

00:53:16.130 --> 00:53:19.060
