[Hae-in?]

00:53:55.110 --> 00:53:57.900
[I made this mille-feuille myself.
Hope you enjoy it.]

00:53:58.450 --> 00:54:03.260
[It's a dessert as sweet as you!
From: Oppa's Manito]

00:54:03.520 --> 00:54:05.850
[The plate needs to be recycled. Hahaha]

00:54:06.240 --> 00:54:09.150
[After reading this one letter,
he's more curious about the next one]

00:54:09.610 --> 00:54:12.430
[Jung Hae-in, do you usually eat on time?]

00:54:12.760 --> 00:54:16.790
[Please share with the staff!
P.S.: Your Manito Bro]

00:54:17.090 --> 00:54:20.240
[Wait a second… I have two Manitos?]

00:54:20.590 --> 00:54:22.240
[A perfect dual personality]

00:54:23.260 --> 00:54:25.030
[Wow, but the mille-feuille is amazing~]

00:54:25.620 --> 00:54:27.050
[Jung Hae-in: How can you
make this yourself…]

00:54:27.050 --> 00:54:28.770
[Jung Hae-in: There's even
gold dust on it!]

00:54:30.540 --> 00:54:32.240
[The appearance makes you go "wow"]

00:54:32.240 --> 00:54:33.040
This is crazy.

00:54:33.860 --> 00:54:37.060
[Takes a bite immediately]

00:54:37.560 --> 00:54:40.230
[His face says it all about the taste]

00:54:40.650 --> 00:54:43.880
[Takes a big bite immediately]

00:54:45.280 --> 00:54:45.560
[Jung Hae-in: Wow.
But if it's at this level]

00:54:45.560 --> 00:54:46.960
But if it's at this level,

00:54:48.110 --> 00:54:52.550
[Jung Hae-in: he's really
a talented pastry chef.]

00:54:53.170 --> 00:54:56.440
[Jung Hae-in: The chocolate here
even has the Manito symbol on it!]

00:54:56.740 --> 00:54:56.950
[Touched by the thoughtful details]

00:54:56.950 --> 00:54:58.120
Thank you so much.

00:54:59.160 --> 00:55:01.740
[Jung Hae-in: The plate actually
looks quite expensive.]

00:55:01.740 --> 00:55:03.170
[Jung Hae-in: I'll make sure
to return it properly~]

00:55:03.170 --> 00:55:05.940
[But I need to know who it is
in order to return it. Hahaha.]

00:55:05.940 --> 00:55:07.760
[After reading the letter] [Jung Hae-in:
The staff must have got some too, right?]

00:55:11.730 --> 00:55:14.060
[Found it nearby right away]

00:55:14.800 --> 00:55:16.460
[Wow~]

00:55:17.350 --> 00:55:19.080
[Please take care of Hae-in! Please enjoy!
These snacks are for the staff!]

00:55:19.080 --> 00:55:20.810
[A warm heart that also
reaches those around him]

00:55:21.370 --> 00:55:23.080
[Jung Hae-in: Awesome…]

00:55:24.470 --> 00:55:26.370
[So many financiers]
[Wow… When was this made?]

00:55:26.370 --> 00:55:28.140
[My Manito is…]

00:55:28.320 --> 00:55:30.780
[A cafe owner?]

00:55:31.790 --> 00:55:34.010
[Oh, so cold]

00:55:34.550 --> 00:55:38.000
[Meanwhile, a person who doesn't look like
a cafe owner is approaching]

00:55:39.760 --> 00:55:40.630
[Sighs… So excited]

00:55:40.630 --> 00:55:41.580
I'm so excited.

00:55:43.380 --> 00:55:43.500
I generally don't eat while shooting.

00:55:43.500 --> 00:55:44.540
[He's still praising the mille-feuille]

00:55:44.540 --> 00:55:47.400
But this is really delicious.
Try it. It's amazing.

00:55:47.880 --> 00:55:49.450
[(Name Not Revealed):
Your delivery has arrived.] [Oh, what?]

00:55:49.600 --> 00:55:51.470
[Oh, you scared me.]

00:55:52.090 --> 00:55:54.390
[I'm here to deliver food.]

00:55:54.780 --> 00:55:54.890
How have you been?

00:55:54.890 --> 00:55:56.510
[Here comes a Manito senior]

00:55:56.510 --> 00:55:57.140
Goodness!

00:55:57.910 --> 00:55:58.460
Thank you!

00:55:58.460 --> 00:56:00.520
[Dex: Thank you for having me, Hae-in.]

00:56:00.520 --> 00:56:02.860
[Jung Hae-in: My reliable backup is here.]

00:56:02.860 --> 00:56:04.920
[Dex: How do I look, Hae-in?]

00:56:06.120 --> 00:56:06.480
You look quite like it.

00:56:06.480 --> 00:56:07.210
[Cargo pants, vest, and helmet]

00:56:07.210 --> 00:56:09.220
Perfect. If you wear the helmet,

00:56:09.380 --> 00:56:09.880
you won't be recognized at all.

00:56:09.880 --> 00:56:10.740
[The perfect look of a delivery man]
[This is mine.]

00:56:10.740 --> 00:56:11.540
Is this yours?

00:56:12.000 --> 00:56:12.460
[This is mine.]

00:56:12.460 --> 00:56:13.450
I brought mine.

00:56:14.320 --> 00:56:16.530
[Dex: I also brought this,
a balaclava hat.]

00:56:17.020 --> 00:56:17.840
[Perfect]

00:56:17.840 --> 00:56:19.850
[Dex: Wearing the balaclava hat
and the helmet?]

00:56:20.150 --> 00:56:22.060
[Dex: You wouldn't know who it was
even if I took off the helmet.]

00:56:22.060 --> 00:56:23.620
[Dex: Because you can only see the eyes.]

00:56:23.850 --> 00:56:25.840
[Jung Hae-in: But your eyes
are way too distinctive.]

00:56:25.840 --> 00:56:27.020
[Jung Hae-in: I can tell right away
who you are.]

00:56:27.020 --> 00:56:27.990
I'll wear my helmet to cover them then.

00:56:27.990 --> 00:56:28.050
-Sit down first.
-I did this on purpose.

00:56:28.050 --> 00:56:30.710
[Sit down first
and make a strategy briefing]

00:56:30.710 --> 00:56:32.540
[What's this?]
[Jung Hae-in: No, I have an order…]

00:56:32.540 --> 00:56:33.320
What's this?

00:56:33.570 --> 00:56:36.180
[Jung Hae-in: I was doing the shooting.
My Manito sent it here and left.]

00:56:36.180 --> 00:56:36.720
This?

00:56:36.780 --> 00:56:37.340
This and the mille-feuille
were made by him.

00:56:37.340 --> 00:56:38.520
[Can't wait to show off
the gift from his Manito]

00:56:38.520 --> 00:56:39.200
What?

00:56:39.700 --> 00:56:40.560
And the letter.

00:56:40.800 --> 00:56:41.930
[To Jung Hae-in: Do you eat on time?
Thanks for your work in shooting the ad.]

00:56:41.930 --> 00:56:42.350
[You should take care of those
around you at times like this.]

00:56:42.350 --> 00:56:43.060
[Share it with the staff! P.S. Your Manito
Bro] [Dex: Wait, it says "Manito Bro."]

00:56:43.060 --> 00:56:45.540
[P.S.: Your Manito Bro] [Dex: But
it looks like a woman's handwriting.]

00:56:45.540 --> 00:56:46.070
I know, right?

00:56:46.070 --> 00:56:48.220
[Jung Hae-in: And it says "Oppa" here.]

00:56:48.220 --> 00:56:49.720
[Dex: Oh, really?]

00:56:49.720 --> 00:56:49.970
[From: Oppa's Manito]
[Jung Hae-in: So this is a smokescreen.]

00:56:49.970 --> 00:56:51.670
So this is a smokescreen.

00:56:51.840 --> 00:56:52.480
Smokescreen.

00:56:52.480 --> 00:56:53.280
Smokescreen.

00:56:54.560 --> 00:56:56.370
[Dex: Then who's your Manito?]

00:56:57.050 --> 00:57:00.620
[Ears perked up]
[Jung Hae-in: My Manito is…]

00:57:01.320 --> 00:57:05.180
[Actress Go Younjung]

00:57:05.350 --> 00:57:07.610
[Dex: I want to meet her in person too…]
[Chuckling]

00:57:07.610 --> 00:57:08.140
Then, today, let's just…

00:57:08.140 --> 00:57:09.950
[Thank you]

00:57:10.140 --> 00:57:10.270
Thank you.

00:57:10.270 --> 00:57:11.810
[The delivery is already worth it]

00:57:11.810 --> 00:57:13.140
A dramatic compromise.

00:57:13.790 --> 00:57:17.180
[Jung Hae-in: But I know
she's very generous and straightforward.]

00:57:18.140 --> 00:57:20.220
[Dex: She's known for
being generous and straightforward.]

00:57:20.220 --> 00:57:22.610
[Dex: And she's quite easygoing.]

00:57:22.610 --> 00:57:24.740
[Jung Hae-in: She's more impulsive
than I thought.]

00:57:24.740 --> 00:57:25.220
Really?

00:57:25.220 --> 00:57:27.380
[Jung Hae-in: I was wearing
a helmet like you.]

00:57:27.380 --> 00:57:29.200
[Jung Hae-in: I said it was
a flash delivery and gave it to her.]

00:57:29.200 --> 00:57:31.880
[So did she catch you?]
[Jung Hae-in: Then she ran towards me.]

00:57:31.880 --> 00:57:33.270
[Jung Hae-in: She didn't catch me.
I ran away when I saw her.]

00:57:33.270 --> 00:57:34.530
-You ran?
-I ran away when I saw her.

00:57:34.530 --> 00:57:37.190
[Wait, what if my helmet gets pulled off?]

00:57:38.790 --> 00:57:39.210
OK.

00:57:39.210 --> 00:57:41.860
[Dex: What's the gift
that I need to deliver?]

00:57:41.860 --> 00:57:45.520
[Ah, there's a mission?]
[Jung Hae-in: You have a mission.]

00:57:45.710 --> 00:57:45.830
[Younjung likes peaches]

00:57:45.830 --> 00:57:48.150
Actress Go likes peaches.

00:57:48.160 --> 00:57:48.690
Peaches?

00:57:48.730 --> 00:57:49.410
So there's a cafe
famous for peaches in Seongsu-dong.

00:57:49.410 --> 00:57:51.850
[Knows Younjung well
and searched for the cafe]

00:57:51.850 --> 00:57:52.680
I found it.

00:57:52.930 --> 00:57:53.410
-You go buy the peach parfait.
-Parfait.

00:57:53.410 --> 00:57:54.840
[Shopping List: ① Peach Parfait;
② Coffee; ③ Peach Shaved Ice]

00:57:54.840 --> 00:57:56.330
She also likes drinking coffee.

00:57:56.330 --> 00:57:57.420
Coffee.

00:57:57.520 --> 00:57:59.060
And you need to buy peach shaved ice.

00:57:59.060 --> 00:58:00.360
Shaved ice. Coffee.

00:58:00.860 --> 00:58:03.820
[Jung Hae-in: Say "Your Manito asked me
to give this to you." Then hand it over.]

00:58:04.070 --> 00:58:06.400
[Should I say "Your Manito asked me
to give it to you"?]

00:58:06.400 --> 00:58:06.650
[That way, even if my identity
is uncovered, it won't cause confusion…]

00:58:06.650 --> 00:58:08.510
Even if my identity
is uncovered…

00:58:08.530 --> 00:58:09.680
-No.
-It won't cause confusion.

00:58:09.680 --> 00:58:13.050
[Aha~ Manito would hide his identity]

00:58:13.050 --> 00:58:15.160
Manitos can pretend they are not Manitos.

00:58:15.160 --> 00:58:18.790
[Dex: You've become a professional
after only one day.]

00:58:18.790 --> 00:58:20.410
[Jung Hae-in: I need you
to deliver my letter.]

00:58:20.610 --> 00:58:20.710
[Also gives him the letter
written in advance]

00:58:20.710 --> 00:58:22.130
-This is the letter I wrote.
-I'll make sure…

00:58:22.130 --> 00:58:22.780
I'll make sure to deliver them properly.

00:58:22.780 --> 00:58:25.300
[It's okay. You can read it. It's fine.]
[Dex: I won't read the letter.]

00:58:25.300 --> 00:58:26.740
[It's okay. You can read it. It's fine.]
[I'm so curious?]

00:58:26.790 --> 00:58:28.440
[Hello. I'm your Manito~]

00:58:28.520 --> 00:58:30.980
[I knew you ran
but I didn't expect you ran this fast.]

00:58:31.260 --> 00:58:33.780
[Dex: There's still a surprise coming.
From: Your Manito]

00:58:33.780 --> 00:58:35.310
[I'm leaving then, Bro.]

00:58:35.310 --> 00:58:36.240
-Go for it!
-Go for it!

00:58:36.240 --> 00:58:36.370
[Go for it, Dex!]
[Go for it, Jung Hae-in!]

00:58:36.370 --> 00:58:38.240
-Go for it, Dex!
-Go for it, Jung Hae-in!

00:58:38.240 --> 00:58:38.660
-Come on!
-Come on!

00:58:38.660 --> 00:58:41.050
[Leaves after cheering each other on]

00:58:41.160 --> 00:58:41.420
[(To Dex) I'll send him the location]

00:58:41.420 --> 00:58:42.950
I'll send him the location.

00:58:45.700 --> 00:58:46.370
So cold.

00:58:47.540 --> 00:58:49.270
[Shivering]

00:58:50.620 --> 00:58:54.250
[Oh? It's Hae-in.]
[Setting out on the mission]

00:58:54.250 --> 00:58:54.890
Hey, Bro.

00:58:55.200 --> 00:58:57.310
[Jinyoung!]
[Yes, I'm off.]

00:58:57.310 --> 00:59:00.090
[Get some for the staff too.
You can decide what to buy.]

00:59:00.090 --> 00:59:03.030
[It's better to buy some bread
or something good to eat together.]

00:59:03.340 --> 00:59:03.940
Okay, Bro.

00:59:03.960 --> 00:59:06.070
[Around 1,000,000 KRW
should do it, right?]

00:59:06.070 --> 00:59:09.060
[Um, then… Well…
I'll transfer the money to you.]

00:59:09.060 --> 00:59:10.160
No, I don't mean that.

00:59:10.160 --> 00:59:12.700
[Yeah, go for it.]
[I'll only buy more, never less.]

00:59:12.700 --> 00:59:13.220
Okay.

00:59:13.250 --> 00:59:15.380
[Dex: I'll just do as you say,
no questions asked.]

00:59:15.380 --> 00:59:18.200
[If anything comes up later,
I'll handle it.]

00:59:18.200 --> 00:59:19.020
I see.

00:59:19.020 --> 00:59:20.680
[I'll report to you later~ Biong!]

00:59:20.680 --> 00:59:21.670
-Yeah.
-Biong!

00:59:22.200 --> 00:59:22.880
Biong!

00:59:25.190 --> 00:59:27.110
[Dex: Actually, our team also…]

00:59:27.110 --> 00:59:30.020
[Dex: We worked together for 4 or 5 days.]

00:59:30.400 --> 00:59:34.690
[And we've gotten closer.]

00:59:35.070 --> 00:59:38.010
[We would send gifts to each other
after the shooting too.]

00:59:38.250 --> 00:59:40.770
[Dex: Jennie did a lot for me.]

00:59:41.290 --> 00:59:48.750
[I would prepare what she likes
and send it to her.]

00:59:49.070 --> 00:59:52.610
[Dex: It's very interesting.
Even after the shooting…]

00:59:52.890 --> 00:59:56.580
[I would go to the studio,
drop my gift, and leave. Hahaha.]

00:59:56.580 --> 00:59:59.600
[Laughing]

00:59:59.770 --> 01:00:02.200
[Dex: These are all my Manito activities.]

01:00:02.200 --> 01:00:04.520
[There aren't even
any cameras capturing them.]

01:00:05.390 --> 01:00:05.580
["The Secret Friends Club" makes people
feel the joy of giving to each other]

01:00:05.580 --> 01:00:09.510
It's like a memory
that only we'll ever understand.

01:00:12.020 --> 01:00:13.820
[I think this is the place?]

01:00:15.190 --> 01:00:15.780
[Arrives at the cafe Hae-in found]

01:00:15.780 --> 01:00:17.380
So this is what it looks like.

01:00:17.490 --> 01:00:18.570
Hello.

01:00:20.050 --> 01:00:22.740
[Dex: This is my first time
buying a whole box of coffee.]

01:00:24.220 --> 01:00:26.220
[Gotta secure it like this]

01:00:26.500 --> 01:00:28.340
[Okay, let's go. Hurry up.]

01:00:29.010 --> 01:00:30.290
[Before it gets cold!]

01:00:33.280 --> 01:00:35.560
[Dex: Let me practice my lines a bit.]

01:00:35.710 --> 01:00:37.730
[Your Manito sent me here.]

01:00:37.840 --> 01:00:40.530
[Your Manito sent me here.]

01:00:41.510 --> 01:00:43.270
[I think she'll find this
more exciting, hahaha.]

01:00:43.270 --> 01:00:44.060
[Who are you?]

01:00:44.060 --> 01:00:45.150
She might say that.

01:00:45.870 --> 01:00:47.640
[Slants]

01:00:48.240 --> 01:00:51.730
[The adjacent car cut in dangerously]

01:00:54.330 --> 01:00:56.000
[That person really…]

01:00:58.310 --> 01:01:01.110
[Oh no! Because of the sudden stop]

01:01:01.510 --> 01:01:03.760
[I'm afraid the coffee would spill out.]

01:01:04.110 --> 01:01:08.520
[Ah… I really…]

01:01:09.720 --> 01:01:09.870
[Sad]

01:01:09.870 --> 01:01:11.430
I don't know if that person
is older or younger than me,

01:01:11.430 --> 01:01:12.140
or at the same age as me,

01:01:12.140 --> 01:01:13.620
but this wasn't right, was it?

01:01:13.620 --> 01:01:14.940
[Beep]

01:01:14.940 --> 01:01:16.480
[Beep] [Be quiet]

01:01:17.120 --> 01:01:18.610
OK.

01:01:19.030 --> 01:01:21.700
[Oh no… (crying face)]

01:01:23.430 --> 01:01:25.730
[Dex: We're almost there.
What should I do?]

01:01:27.610 --> 01:01:29.610
[Younjung is busy
with the poster shooting]

01:01:29.610 --> 01:01:30.360
Very pretty.

01:01:32.240 --> 01:01:33.030
Okay.

01:01:34.360 --> 01:01:35.010
[Arrives at Younjung's shooting location]

01:01:35.010 --> 01:01:36.490
Is it here? On the right.

01:01:38.170 --> 01:01:39.520
It's here.

01:01:42.520 --> 01:01:43.940
[I'm so nervous…]

01:01:44.600 --> 01:01:46.740
[Coffee, I hope you're fine…]

01:01:53.180 --> 01:01:58.860
[A mess in the trunk…]

01:02:01.630 --> 01:02:05.740
[Exhausted]

01:02:06.440 --> 01:02:09.250
[Younjung, reading the HQ's messages,
doesn't know anything]

01:02:09.250 --> 01:02:10.080
So cute.

01:02:10.240 --> 01:02:12.180
[Uh…]

01:02:12.400 --> 01:02:14.960
[Go Younjung: The gift
that Frog received was made by…]

01:02:15.660 --> 01:02:18.120
[Who was it?]

01:02:18.120 --> 01:02:21.510
[Go Younjung: Looks like
Lion made the dessert.]

01:02:23.850 --> 01:02:25.450
Because this is the logo of Manito, right?

01:02:25.450 --> 01:02:28.040
[Noticed the logo of Manito]

01:02:28.040 --> 01:02:29.330
Our red one.

01:02:30.290 --> 01:02:30.950
Gosh.

01:02:31.270 --> 01:02:33.630
[Go Younjung: Luckily I didn't do it.
I almost made the same thing.]

01:02:35.100 --> 01:02:36.650
[I was planning to do baking.]

01:02:36.650 --> 01:02:37.240
Really?

01:02:37.250 --> 01:02:39.020
[But this is too good…]

01:02:39.600 --> 01:02:39.740
[Amazing]

01:02:39.740 --> 01:02:41.800
They actually made a mille-feuille.

01:02:42.840 --> 01:02:45.990
[I can't get caught today.] [Meanwhile,
Jinkyung is on her way to Hae-in]

01:02:47.090 --> 01:02:48.510
[Suddenly]

01:02:49.060 --> 01:02:49.280
Thirty-two. Are we almost there?

01:02:49.280 --> 01:02:50.530
[Getting closer in a flash; Hong Jinkyung,
Jung Hae-in, Seongdong District]

01:02:50.530 --> 01:02:52.190
Only two minutes left, right?

01:02:52.620 --> 01:02:55.750
[Hong Jinkyung: I shouldn't be like this.
I have to dress up, right?]

01:02:56.820 --> 01:02:59.790
[Well… I only have this kind of wig.]

01:02:59.790 --> 01:03:02.390
[(For example) This kind]

01:03:02.390 --> 01:03:03.400
[It's a little scary, isn't it?]

01:03:03.400 --> 01:03:05.840
[Scary]

01:03:06.430 --> 01:03:08.170
[Or besides this…]

01:03:08.170 --> 01:03:09.430
[There's this too!]

01:03:09.430 --> 01:03:12.730
[Which one is better? Sapsali hairstyle]

01:03:13.240 --> 01:03:14.020
The one just now?

01:03:14.020 --> 01:03:14.810
This one is better.

01:03:14.810 --> 01:03:15.790
[Decided to choose
the cuter(?) Sapsali hairstyle]

01:03:15.790 --> 01:03:16.990
Right? This one then.

01:03:18.720 --> 01:03:20.620
[Hong Jinkyung: Should I wear a mask?]

01:03:21.220 --> 01:03:23.020
[The disguise is getting
greedier and greedier]

01:03:23.020 --> 01:03:23.690
Like this.

01:03:25.010 --> 01:03:27.390
[Face covered completely—fully armed]

01:03:27.730 --> 01:03:30.430
[Phone case]
[Going to meet Jinkyung after packaging]

01:03:31.030 --> 01:03:31.430
[Planning to take a taxi
to deliver the gift]

01:03:31.430 --> 01:03:32.230
Is that a taxi?

01:03:32.720 --> 01:03:33.780
Let's go. Let's go.

01:03:34.380 --> 01:03:35.840
Hello.

01:03:36.760 --> 01:03:37.490
Oh, Jinkyung is in Seongsu-dong.

01:03:37.490 --> 01:03:40.380
[Jinkyung is in Seongsu-dong!
She's entering Seoul Forest.]

01:03:40.380 --> 01:03:41.910
She's at Seoul Forest Park.

01:03:42.520 --> 01:03:42.940
[Hong Jinkyung; Seongdong District;
