01:27:47.780 --> 01:27:47.960
[What on earth?]

01:27:47.960 --> 01:27:48.460
That person! Catch her immediately!

01:27:48.460 --> 01:27:49.580
[Catch her!]

01:27:49.660 --> 01:27:49.740
[The situation is reversed!
Now it's an escape?]

01:27:49.740 --> 01:27:50.550
Run!

01:27:51.460 --> 01:27:52.700
[Stop right there!]

01:27:52.860 --> 01:27:53.190
[A game of hide-and-seek with gifts,
chasing, and being chased]

01:27:53.190 --> 01:27:54.400
What's going on?

01:27:55.670 --> 01:27:56.620
Applying the disguise now.

01:27:56.620 --> 01:27:58.300
[Hae-in x Dex:
Secret Assistant Operation]

01:27:58.300 --> 01:28:00.100
[Secret Assistant's target: Go Younjung]

01:28:00.340 --> 01:28:00.380
[Eating without a clue of what's to come]

01:28:00.380 --> 01:28:01.440
I like eating this.

01:28:01.710 --> 01:28:02.620
This is conger eel.

01:28:02.620 --> 01:28:04.740
[This was sent by your Manito.]

01:28:04.820 --> 01:28:06.140
[Hey!]

01:28:06.540 --> 01:28:08.180
[My phone! My phone!]

01:28:08.360 --> 01:28:09.820
-Who are you? -This is from your Manito.

01:28:09.820 --> 01:28:10.050
[Did the mission just fail?]

01:28:10.050 --> 01:28:11.330
I messed it up.

01:28:11.340 --> 01:28:12.860
[I haven't finished delivering my gifts yet.]

01:28:14.450 --> 01:28:15.400
When?

01:28:15.460 --> 01:28:16.420
[Pretending not to know]

01:28:16.800 --> 01:28:16.860
Dubai chewy cookies.

01:28:16.860 --> 01:28:17.620
[Delivery complete to the Di-Madman]

01:28:17.620 --> 01:28:19.500
I wanted to give it to her at the very end.

01:28:19.500 --> 01:28:22.660
[Finally revealing the identity of the Manito!]

01:28:22.740 --> 01:28:23.940
[Was this all made with ingredients from home?]

01:28:24.020 --> 01:28:24.240
[A surge of curiosity]

01:28:24.240 --> 01:28:25.740
Even the caviar and sea urchin?

01:28:25.740 --> 01:28:25.910
[The caviar and sea urchin...]

01:28:25.910 --> 01:28:27.060
I didn't send the caviar and sea urchin.

01:28:27.060 --> 01:28:28.900
[I didn't send that...]
[What?]

01:28:29.060 --> 01:28:29.340
Hello.

01:28:29.340 --> 01:28:30.660
[The unexpected appearance of Catfish]

01:28:30.660 --> 01:28:31.710
Chef Yoon Namno.

01:28:31.860 --> 01:28:31.880
[Together with the master
of handmade crafts]

01:28:31.880 --> 01:28:33.780
I am truly shocked.

01:28:33.780 --> 01:28:33.920
[Secret Manito Operation]

01:28:33.920 --> 01:28:35.220
Our Manito seniors: the firefighters.

01:28:35.220 --> 01:28:36.300
[Secret Manito: The Fire Department]

01:28:36.540 --> 01:28:37.130
[Fucheon Fire Station]
[Delivering the joy of giving]

01:28:37.130 --> 01:28:38.300
You will all take part in the Secret Manito project,

01:28:38.300 --> 01:28:39.300
[to the world]

01:28:39.580 --> 01:28:39.750
[The Final Table: The last hurdle
to becoming an official member]

01:28:39.750 --> 01:28:41.670
delivering the joy of giving to the world.

01:28:41.670 --> 01:28:42.880
Fucheon Fire Station.

01:28:42.880 --> 01:28:42.980
We are going to do some handmade cooking.

01:28:42.980 --> 01:28:44.360
[Under the master chef, Namno's guidance]

01:28:44.360 --> 01:28:45.780
Then roll it one more time.

01:28:45.780 --> 01:28:48.350
[Let's develop a new menu!]

01:28:48.350 --> 01:28:49.750
OK, looks good, looks good.

01:28:49.750 --> 01:28:50.420
Nice job!

01:28:50.580 --> 01:28:50.690
[Swaying]
[Why is Younjung so happy during the cooking?]

01:28:50.690 --> 01:28:52.420
Can you show that one more time?

01:28:55.540 --> 01:28:57.380
[Here they are! Here they are!]

01:28:57.380 --> 01:28:58.420
[So nervous...]

01:28:58.540 --> 01:28:59.290
[Secret Manito: D-DAY]

01:28:59.290 --> 01:29:00.040
What is this?

01:29:00.450 --> 01:29:01.600
I am confident I can do a good job.

01:29:01.600 --> 01:29:02.800
Fighting! Fighting!

01:29:02.830 --> 01:29:03.830
We'll do our best.

01:29:03.860 --> 01:29:04.330
[A meal handmade for the Secret Manito]

01:29:04.330 --> 01:29:05.230
It looks so tempting.

01:29:05.230 --> 01:29:06.790
As expected, it takes a professional to do this.

01:29:06.790 --> 01:29:07.660
It must be delicious.

01:29:07.660 --> 01:29:08.650
Wonderful!

01:29:08.940 --> 01:29:10.580
[I'm digging in!]

01:29:10.940 --> 01:29:13.740
[Anticipation]

01:29:13.740 --> 01:29:14.780
[Wow, it smells so good]

01:29:14.780 --> 01:29:18.380
[Emergency broadcast: Fire dispatch!]

01:29:18.780 --> 01:29:21.220
[Non-stop emergency dispatches]

01:29:21.320 --> 01:29:21.380
They left before they even finished eating?

01:29:21.380 --> 01:29:23.060
[Will they be able
to deliver the gifts successfully?]

01:29:23.060 --> 01:29:23.960
What should we do?